creator: Flipp Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Flipp helps you save up to 50% on your weekly shopping. Simple! This essential app brings you the latest flyers and deals from more than 2000 of your favourite retailers including Walmart, Sobeys, and Shopper’s Drug Mart to help you save money. You’ll also find a variety of online offers to stay on budget. Best of all, it’s completely FREE!

This all-in-one app helps you along every step of your shopping journey, from planning to checkout, and everything in between. Find your flyers, saved offers, shopping list, and loyalty cards in one place, so you don’t have to scramble at the checkout.

Wave goodbye to inconvenient paper flyers and junk mail, and take your deal hunting on-the-go with Flipp!

Here’s why Flipp is more than just a flyer app:

- Find relevant deals and flyers from stores near you.

- Explore up-to-date flyers and offers from over 2000 of your favourite retailers.

- Instantly search and find sales for items you want with our powerful search feature.

- “Clip” or save deals to your shopping list, so you can have them on hand at all times.

- Find value at a large variety of retailers including grocery, pharmacy, electronics, general merchandise, fashion, and pets.

- Discover flyer and online deals by categories like electronics, home & garden, apparel and more.

- Add your store loyalty or rewards cards so you don’t forget to use them at checkout, and take advantage of all your rewards points.

- Create your shopping list right on Flipp. Have your list, deals, and saved offers all in one place.

We’re always adding new stores! Discover value and savings at popular stores including:

- Walmart
- Best Buy
- The Home Depot
- Canadian Tire
- Shopper’s Drug Mart
- Metro
- Sobeys


Once you try Flipp, you’ll never want to shop without it. But don’t take it from us!

Here’s what the experts are saying about Flipp:

The best part about this app, in my opinion, is that it renders the best deals nearby, even when I’m travelling – Lesley-Anne Scorgie, The Toronto Star

If you don't want to store stacks of retail ads, utilize Flipp to eliminate clutter...maximizing savings in a few taps on your phone – Andrea Woroch, U.S. News & World Report

Love Flipp too? Leave us a review!

Have any questions or suggestions? Contact us at flipp.force.com

title: Flipp - Weekly Shopping

creator: Flipp Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Browse thousands of flyers digitally with the Flipp app, and find deals from over 2000 stores including Walmart, Shoppers, Canadian Tire and more. Flipp makes it easy to save money on groceries, pharmacy, and other household essentials.

Download the Flipp app for free and see what’s on sale this week at stores near you.

Here’s what our users love about Flipp:

- Local deals, always up to date
No need to wait for paper flyers to arrive in the mail. With Flipp, your flyers arrive on time, on the app. Flipp uses your location to find deals from stores near you — so you’re always getting relevant and dependable information.

- Wide variety of content
In addition to weekly grocery deals, Flipp finds you deals on pharmacy, home & garden, electronics, pet supplies, and more.

- Quickly search for what you need
Flipp’s powerful search feature quickly scans all available flyers to tell you where you can get the items you need on sale. You can also search for stores to find a retailer’s flyer right when you need it.

- Save deals by clipping
See a deal you like? Simply clip the deal to your shopping list, and come back to it later when you need it.

- Add favourites
Add stores to your favourites to access your frequent flyers from one convenient tab.

- Stay organized with your shopping list
We always have our phones on hand these days, so why not use the in-app shopping list to keep track of items you need? The Flipp shopping list will scan all available flyers, and find you offers for the items on your list.

- See what’s trending
Never miss out on a hot deal. Check out the Deals tab to see the top trending deals in your area.

- Save with friends
Find a deal on Flipp that’s too good to keep to yourself? Share it with friends and family. You can also share your shopping list with your shopping partner to keep track of the items you need, together.

- All your loyalty cards in one place
Never miss out on your loyalty points and rewards. Add your store loyalty cards to your Flipp app to quickly access your cards during checkout.

Download the Flipp app now to start saving on your weekly shopping!

Have any questions or suggestions? Contact us at flipp.force.com

Introducing Dark Mode! Choose between “Light” (classic), “Dark”, or “System” for your preferred browsing experience. Choosing “System” will follow the settings you’ve set for your device. To change between modes go to Settings, then Theme.

Branding update. We cleaned up the colours throughout the app for a modern, sleek look and improved accessibility. Updates include:
• App icon in new brand colour
• Updated startup screen
• Title bar colour

title: Flipp - Weekly Shopping

creator: Flipp Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Browse thousands of flyers digitally with the Flipp app, and find deals from over 2000 stores including Walmart, Shoppers, Canadian Tire and more. Flipp makes it easy to save money on groceries, pharmacy, and other household essentials.

Download the Flipp app for free and see what’s on sale this week at stores near you.

Here’s what our users love about Flipp:

-LOCAL DEALS, ALWAYS UP TO DATE
No need to wait for paper flyers to arrive in the mail. With Flipp, your flyers arrive on time, on the app. Flipp uses your location to find deals from stores near you — so you’re always getting relevant and dependable information.

-WIDE VARIETY OF CONTENT
In addition to weekly grocery deals, Flipp finds you deals on pharmacy, home & garden, electronics, pet supplies, and more.

-QUICKLY SEARCH FOR WHAT YOU NEED
Flipp’s powerful search feature quickly scans all available flyers to tell you where you can get the items you need on sale. You can also search for stores to find a retailer’s flyer right when you need it.

-KEEP TRACK OF DEALS WITH WATCH LIST
Watch List is the easiest way to track the deals you want. Add groceries, brands, or even big-ticket items to your Watch List and let Flipp get to work to find you the best deals.

-SAVE DEALS BY CLIPPING
See a deal you like? Simply clip the deal to your shopping list, and come back to it later when you need it.

-ADD FAVOURITES
Add stores to your favourites to access your frequent flyers from one convenient tab.

-STAY ORGANIZED WITH YOUR SHOPPING LIST
We always have our phones on hand these days, so why not use the in-app shopping list to keep track of items you need? The Flipp shopping list will scan all available flyers, and find you offers for the items on your list.

-SEE WHAT’S TRENDING
Never miss out on a hot deal. Check out the Deals tab to see the top trending deals in your area.

-SAVE WITH FRIENDS
Find a deal on Flipp that’s too good to keep to yourself? Share it with friends and family. You can also share your shopping list with your shopping partner to keep track of the items you need, together.

-ALL YOUR LOYALTY CARDS IN ONE PLACE
Never miss out on your loyalty points and rewards. Add your store loyalty cards to your Flipp app to quickly access your cards during checkout.

Download the Flipp app now to start saving on your weekly shopping!

Have any questions or suggestions? Contact us at flipp.force.com

Download the Flipp app for free and see what’s on sale this week at stores near you.

Here’s what our users love about Flipp:

-LOCAL DEALS, ALWAYS UP TO DATE
No need to wait for paper flyers to arrive in the mail. With Flipp, your flyers arrive on time, on the app. Flipp uses your location to find deals from stores near you — so you’re always getting relevant and dependable information.

-WIDE VARIETY OF CONTENT
In addition to weekly grocery deals, Flipp finds you deals on pharmacy, home & garden, electronics, pet supplies, and more.

-QUICKLY SEARCH FOR WHAT YOU NEED
Flipp’s powerful search feature quickly scans all available flyers to tell you where you can get the items you need on sale. You can also search for stores to find a retailer’s flyer right when you need it.

-KEEP TRACK OF DEALS WITH WATCH LIST
Watch List is the easiest way to track the deals you want. Add groceries, brands, or even big-ticket items to your Watch List and let Flipp get to work to find you the best deals.

-SAVE DEALS BY CLIPPING
See a deal you like? Simply clip the deal to your shopping list, and come back to it later when you need it.

-ADD FAVOURITES
Add stores to your favourites to access your frequent flyers from one convenient tab.

-STAY ORGANIZED WITH YOUR SHOPPING LIST
We always have our phones on hand these days, so why not use the in-app shopping list to keep track of items you need? The Flipp shopping list will scan all available flyers, and find you offers for the items on your list.

-SAVE WITH FRIENDS
Find a deal on Flipp that’s too good to keep to yourself? Share it with friends and family. You can also share your shopping list with your shopping partner to keep track of the items you need, together.

-ALL YOUR LOYALTY CARDS IN ONE PLACE
Never miss out on your loyalty points and rewards. Add your store loyalty cards to your Flipp app to quickly access your cards during checkout.

Download the Flipp app now to start saving on your weekly shopping!

Have any questions or suggestions? Contact us at flipp.force.com

title: Flipp - Weekly Shopping

creator: Flipp Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Browse thousands of flyers digitally with the Flipp app, and find deals from over 2000 stores including Walmart, Shoppers, Canadian Tire and more. Flipp makes it easy to save money on groceries, pharmacy, and other household essentials.

Download the Flipp app for free and see what’s on sale this week at stores near you.

Here’s what our users love about Flipp:

-LOCAL DEALS, ALWAYS UP TO DATE
No need to wait for paper flyers to arrive in the mail. With Flipp, your flyers arrive on time, on the app. Flipp uses your location to find deals from stores near you — so you’re always getting relevant and dependable information.

-WIDE VARIETY OF CONTENT
In addition to weekly grocery deals, Flipp finds you deals on pharmacy, home & garden, electronics, pet supplies, and more.

-QUICKLY SEARCH FOR WHAT YOU NEED
Flipp’s powerful search feature quickly scans all available flyers to tell you where you can get the items you need on sale. You can also search for stores to find a retailer’s flyer right when you need it.

-KEEP TRACK OF DEALS WITH WATCH LIST
Watch List is the easiest way to track the deals you want. Add groceries, brands, or even big-ticket items to your Watch List and let Flipp get to work to find you the best deals.

-SAVE DEALS BY CLIPPING
See a deal you like? Simply clip the deal to your shopping list, and come back to it later when you need it.

-ADD FAVOURITES
Add stores to your favourites to access your frequent flyers from one convenient tab.

-STAY ORGANIZED WITH YOUR SHOPPING LIST
We always have our phones on hand these days, so why not use the in-app shopping list to keep track of items you need? The Flipp shopping list will scan all available flyers, and find you offers for the items on your list.

-SAVE WITH FRIENDS
Find a deal on Flipp that’s too good to keep to yourself? Share it with friends and family. You can also share your shopping list with your shopping partner to keep track of the items you need, together.

-ALL YOUR LOYALTY CARDS IN ONE PLACE
Never miss out on your loyalty points and rewards. Add your store loyalty cards to your Flipp app to quickly access your cards during checkout.

Download the Flipp app now to start saving on your weekly shopping!

title: Flipp - Weekly Shopping

creator: Flipp Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Be the first to know when new sales drop and easily access weekly ads, circulars, shopping lists, and more to save money every single week. From groceries to home essentials, all the deals you’re looking for can be found on Flipp. No more overspending.

-NEVER MISS A SALE NEAR YOU

With digital ads and circulars from over 2000 retailers across North America, Flipp makes it easy to find all the latest deals near you. Simply pop in your location, select your favorite stores, and start finding the best deals today.

-QUICKLY FIND THE DEALS YOU WANT

Flipp’s Search tool does the heavy lifting for you, letting you compare prices at different stores for the items you need. Filter by favorite stores, ways to shop, and even by date to find exactly what you’re looking for, easier than ever.

-KNOW WHEN NEW DEALS DROP

If something is not on sale right now, don’t worry. Create a Watch List of items you’re interested in, and we’ll immediately notify you when new deals arrive.

-PLAN AHEAD AND STAY ORGANIZED

See what’s on sale now and preview upcoming deals to make the most of your shopping budget. If you see a deal you like, tap to circle it and save it to your shopping list for easy access.

-SAVE EVEN MORE WITH COUPONS

Find digital and print coupons by store and easily redeem them at checkout right from the app.

-COLLABORATE WITH FRIENDS AND FAMILY

Share your shopping list with a friend or family member to collaborate in real time and easily plan together. Found a deal a friend will love? Share it right from the app so no one misses out!


Whether you’re looking to save money on groceries, pharmacy, and other household essentials, Flipp makes it easy to find the best deals near you. Download Flipp today so you don’t miss out on the free app that helps millions of shoppers save money every single week.

Have any questions or suggestions? Contact us at https://help.flipp.com/
descriptionShort: Stop overspending on groceries. Plan ahead with weekly deals to save money.

Download Flipp and see what’s on sale this week at stores near you.

LOCAL DEALS, ALWAYS UP TO DATE

WIDE VARIETY OF CONTENT
In addition to weekly grocery deals, Flipp finds you savings and offers on pharmacy, home & garden, electronics, pet supplies, and more. Discover the best discounts and coupons at your favorite stores like Aldi and Trader Joe's.

QUICKLY SEARCH FOR WHAT YOU NEED
Flipp’s powerful search feature quickly scans all available weekly ads and coupons to tell you where you can get the items you need on sale. You can also search for stores, like Save Mart or Natural Grocers, to find a retailer’s weekly ad right when you need it.

STAY ORGANIZED WITH YOUR SHOPPING LIST
Keep track of items you need with this convenient grocery list. Find weekly deals for items you need, right from your list. Organize your list by retailer and know what to get at each store. Add quantities to items and bring home the right amount. Clip deals from ads directly to your Shopping List with price and valid dates displayed, all in one place.

SAVE DEALS BY CLIPPING
See a deal or discount you like? Simply clip the coupon to your shopping list, and come back to it later when you need it.

ADD FAVORITES

title:

62.0.0

creator: Flipp Operations Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Why have several store apps taking up space when Flipp can find you deals from them all? Flipp is the most powerful app for grocery savings and coupons. Simplify your grocery shopping routine and save money on your final bill. Create your grocery list and plan ahead with weekly ads and grocery coupons from thousands of stores — all in one place!

Saving money while grocery shopping just got a whole lot easier when you can compare food prices from:
- Walmart
- Target
- Albertsons
- Safeway
- Publix

Beyond groceries, Flipp has pharmacy coupons from stores like Walgreens and CVS. And if you love Publix and Family Dollar coupons, you’re in luck because Flipp has them too!

There’s something for everyone on Flipp — from tech lovers to pet parents. Find deals from specialty stores including:
- Best Buy
- Home Depot
- Lowes
- Petco
- Petsmart

We’re always adding new stores to make saving money on shopping simple!

Ready to start saving money with Flipp? Here’s how!

Find ads and deals at nearby stores.
- Find deals from Walmart, Walgreens, Dollar General, and more local stores.
- Bonus! Select your favorite stores to quickly access your go-to grocery ads in one spot.

Search for any item to compare prices at different stores.
- Search for foods like “soda” or “butter” to see which stores have them on sale.
- Search for any grocery store, like Albertsons, Safeway, or Publix, and quickly find their weekly ad.

Save weekly ad deals and grocery coupons to your shopping list.
- “Clip” or circle deals from weekly ads to your grocery list.
- Tap the plus (+) icon straight from search results to save a deal to your shopping list.

Create your digital shopping list.
- Add food or other items to your grocery list and Flipp will show you deals for the items on your list.
- Share and combine shopping lists with a friend so that you can both view and add items to it.

Discover deals by store category.
- Save money on electronics from Best Buy, on pet supplies from Petco and Petsmart, or even on health essentials from Walgreens and Walmart.
- Shop home & garden sales from stores like Home Depot and Lowes.

Save money every week by comparing prices.
- Discover local stores that are new to you in the ‘Explore’ page. You might find a new favorite!
- From your shopping list, tap the arrow to compare prices for that item at different stores.

Get notified when deals drop.
- Don’t see a deal you love right now? Create a Watch List of items to track.
- Flipp will notify you when there are fresh deals for the items on your list.

Simplify your grocery shopping routine and save money with Flipp’s useful features like the smart shopping list, digital coupons, and weekly ads. Deals from thousands of stores including Walmart, Target, Home Depot, and Albertsons are added weekly — so don’t miss out!

If you’re looking to save money on groceries and other essentials, the Flipp app is a must-have. Questions or suggestions? Contact us at https://help.flipp.com/
